{"tid":2262891,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法武肺疫情再失控  今夜起居家令四周","createTime":"2020-10-29T12:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T18:29:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5d11ea724c915ca71c18dd08a40eadb532ec00d1","tid":2262891,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201029/HQNN7XJO65EURIJH7ZHF7ZBAJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201029%2FHQNN7XJO65EURIJH7ZHF7ZBAJY%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=6c06e9b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201029%2FHQNN7XJO65EURIJH7ZHF7ZBAJY%2F&h=d1bbcc30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201029/HQNN7XJO65EURIJH7ZHF7ZBAJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n法武肺疫情再失控 <br />\n今夜起居家令四周<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i7Rs4_1EcFOF1PT2jB3n86Ke2Xs=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TJXCS2XV6JABZL6VLD554XLE6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi7Rs4_1EcFOF1PT2jB3n86Ke2Xs%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTJXCS2XV6JABZL6VLD554XLE6E.jpg&h=cbbb4218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■法國再爆第二波武漢肺炎，防疫宵禁令的巴黎凱旋門，只有零落警車駐守。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲再爆新一波武漢肺炎，法國成最新重災疫區，每日新確診達數萬宗；為遏止「快將失控」的疫情，法總統馬克龍宣佈全國今日午夜起再實行居家限令四周；德國11月初亦開始全國居家一個月，可能有望度過「無疫」聖誕。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：比利時重災區 醫護確診被要求返工<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍周三晚上8時（香港時間今天凌晨3時）向全國講話，相信是頒佈居家令詳情；據知酒吧、餐廳和中學全日關閉，但小學和公。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法國人春天已經居家兩個月，自第二波疫情出現後，全國20多個城市晚上9時起宵禁防疫，涉三分二約4,600萬人口，但。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jZKWL0-wGjGw6nrbqtSf0vfKEAU=/1385x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DTMBI22IR5BJVEZ2XCDHQ6CLYI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjZKWL0-wGjGw6nrbqtSf0vfKEAU%3D%2F1385x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDTMBI22IR5BJVEZ2XCDHQ6CLYI.jpg&h=e1df95c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■里昂醫護人員帶同設備到機場，準備飛到另一醫院抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德下月起全國限聚<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，原本防疫成績理想的德國，近期每日新症都破萬，累計確診40多萬，死者達10,098人，經濟部長更警告新症在本周末有可能突破一天兩萬宗的關口。<br />\n<br />\n總理默克爾有見及此，昨日與各州領袖會面，商討如何加強防疫措施。最。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wSV4jEW-4Lv3xw17qspXdIuZ1ZQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WMNIQWMUCVDZLN6OFK7EFKYFIQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwSV4jEW-4Lv3xw17qspXdIuZ1ZQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWMNIQWMUCVDZLN6OFK7EFKYFIQ.jpg&h=e1ea051e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■疫情爆發後，打工仔多改為居家工作，商區人潮不再。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n措施旨在保護國民<br />\n<br />\n上述防疫措施如何落實，最終由各州自決，東面由左派控制的圖林根曾反對中央建議，相反巴伐利亞則已自行封鎖兩個重災疫區，紐倫堡在內幾區聖誕市集更已取消。默克爾在會後說，明白建議要求很多，但強調措施只是一時，「限制措施旨在保護國民，特別是老弱的一群」，避免數以百萬計人士被摒棄社會之外。<br />\n<br />\n夾在德法中間的小國比利時疫情更令人憂慮，歐洲疾病預防控制中心本周數字顯示，若。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社/法國The Local網站"},{"pid":"994315b8db56d79effef98600f4ba3b69ae2c8b8","tid":2262891,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"疫情發癲人又發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7711ae62c17e8ec21bb3f91bc902206e49c525","tid":2262891,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T12:35:42.000Z","msg":"根本冇可能斷架啦"},{"pid":"f1104a08fbbc4b120f99e2ab0d9fa1375ea081c3","tid":2262891,"uid":161726,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"af7711ae62c17e8ec21bb3f91bc902206e49c525","tid":2262891,"uid":54721,"like":1,"disli